# Style Analyzer Tab

## Lessons from past bugs (MUST follow)
- [x] All imports at TOP of file (no inline `import re`, `import shutil`, etc.)
- [x] Import QMessageBox in UI file from the start
- [x] Use `setMinimumWidth` not `setFixedWidth` for combos/labels
- [x] Use `setSizePolicy(Fixed, Fixed)` for combos that need to be compact
- [x] All variables must be defined before use — no `group_path` mistakes
- [x] Add try-except with log output in all action handlers
- [x] All buttons must have tooltips

## Build Steps
- [x] Create prompt files (overview, detail, synthesis)
- [x] Create core/style_analyzer.py
- [x] Create ui/style_tab.py
- [x] Register tab in main_window.py
- [x] Syntax check all files
- [ ] Verify UI renders correctly (user testing)
